Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野美星 修学旅行回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色友人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}以下皆为北海道著名特产·伪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八花亭的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木制人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是这个我特意带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 吸 呼 吸 试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的清香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了/哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 回去当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就按计划那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是 身体没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在11点的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在站前广场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧 干嘛要问我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好像是放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在白天？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得可疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 他们也认识那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 小夜学姐也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准备要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我倒不觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我可是为了大八木你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被江户川君叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买书路过的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路过路过路过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分百在约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 有事会发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都要坚持到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江学姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也超在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小点声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此 昨天就该问下部长的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 现在这边要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 觉得还是草间老师最理解她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小夜学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车站附近取照片的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很可疑就跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你们在想什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这样组合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 只是路过这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿高跟鞋走这路太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 今年也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先说的话就一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他 怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在从观测会回来的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是差不多这样的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着今年也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母好像很忙 没法抽身过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让你们吃了一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没机会说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爸爸肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到小朔 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得他有一双很宽大的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常开些不知是真是假的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常和美星 有时也和我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也最喜欢美星了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着天空的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为即使我离开这小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇也永远不会变 永远都是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个小镇中消失的就只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的就保持这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肯定在这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小美星说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今年和朔君看到流星了哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「很高兴哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 天全黑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 到我家来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会是个好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的模考太真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还是第一次在校外考呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是近江介绍的一个预备校的模考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学旁边是哪个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是应试战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天部长从近江同学那拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星凌日的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}最近一次是06年11月9号早上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我们也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来迟...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...你们在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 今天要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪 对大家来说 那是才知晓的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是想避开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不知如何面对她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美总是满面笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请各位回到教室后再做讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果开会到这么晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过的这呆掉的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是前天那时交给他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才过了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得已经错过最佳时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送书签做礼物的话 不会被误解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给男生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就这样等到天亮的话 会更难送出去的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里读到过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽早送出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其它任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部这边好像很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君和美星学姐 突然陷入热恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 我现在很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.74,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 我们回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他凝视着美星学姐的时候那疲倦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没出现过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 更没法交给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是今天还没法给他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能占用你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家就有备用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉成与和泉都回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我就这样回去行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是校长像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样子被看见了 明野会不会误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美星她们一个小学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要经过住宅区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也在住宅区那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美星同一个公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 还在啊 伊藤商店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里变公寓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这玩具好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 忍不住就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我啥都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这个小镇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没怎么重温过以前的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 没能更早点到这来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 之前会离开这个小镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好眼镜坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从北海道带回来的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是文化祭的谢礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有很多事情不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的话来找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看到他现在的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是啪啵君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么了 眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你们怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 之后就让我们来送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找你商量一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 今天也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前考试的时候大家还一起复习来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能让他明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让人担心应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出元气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然有几个限制条例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是同意你们使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这次 下不为例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经好好做过调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也问了其它学校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是搞不清 天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我自己来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想帮忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真努力啊 明野一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到最近才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定无意中让她伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美她却...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实却几乎没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在电话里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也只剩这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个大呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做些什么就不能平复的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们也来参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜学姐 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家 怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文文 还有各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是流星雨的团体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可要一起好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为考试忘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是双子座流星雨的极大日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家偷偷准备的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我只想到可以这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是怕天气不好让你失望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这些还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥你身为大龄学姐居然能哭得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 可以缩在被炉里边吃橘子边看星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为我举办观测会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 有很多流星划过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望总有一天美星能和大家一起看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21分30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北河三的方向二等级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星空画卷真梦幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常听小朔说起爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到小朔现在心里还有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不是故意要瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把手牵起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的天空是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气晴朗 很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的力量 这就是爱的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就想说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人没在交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:46.21,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:48.83,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 如白雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:49.67,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
